messages.subject: Double messages
messages.msgSnippet: I ve been getting two of every message on this list.  Does anyone know how to stop this?  It s been like this for months!  I tried going no-mail for a while,
messages.messageBody:
I've been getting two of every message on this list. Does anyone know how
to stop this? It's been like this for months! I tried going no-mail for a
while, switching to digest. Doesn't change. At least in digest there are
less of the duplicate emails in my inbox. But I still have to delete around
all the duplicate emails and I prefer receiving individual emails. I find
that easier to sift through the topics/threads. I know this has happened
before on other lists. Sometimes it just went away. Right now it is
happening on some of my other yahoo lists, but only occasionally and for
some - not all messages.



Any ideas??



Jenny C
